itial magnetic helicity including the\ncase of non-helical fields from the beginning. The tendency of the magnetic\nhelicity density to the maximal helicity case at large evolution times provides\nthe growth of a seed magnetic field to the strongest magnetic fields in\nastrophysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2015 17:42:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 16 May 2015 18:33:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
