n region and fixed-order\nregion, where we make use of the anti-kt jet algorithm. The 1-Jettiness event\nshape can be a powerful probe of nuclear and QCD dynamics at future\nelectron-ion colliders and by analyzing existing HERA data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2015 20:06:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
