m efficient inference given a\nsimple text description of an HMM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2015 21:16:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 May 2015 19:14:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
